<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  
 
  <title>Clash Characters</title>

  <style>
    body {
      background: #380454;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .characters {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 25px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .characters a img {
      width: 150px;
      max-width: 165px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }

    .characters a img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.55);
    }

    .info {
      margin-top: 370px;
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      background: #2B023D;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <h1>Clash Characters</h1>
  <p>Click a character</p>

  <div class="characters">
    <a href="#hog">
      <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS1ZgYJD6AT-W3i63AZErVfUW2BL6wTS92qZg&s" alt="Hog Rider">
    </a>

    <a href="#mk">
      <img src="https://www.vhv.rs/dpng/d/13-134174_clash-royale-mega-knight-hd-png-download.png" alt="Mega Knight">
    </a>

    <a href="#mp">
      <img src="https://us-tuna-sounds-images.voicemod.net/e15fb140-efca-4557-a5d7-da032df8f740-1678972855619.jpg" alt="Mini P.E.K.K.A">
    </a>

    <a href="#larry">
      <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/originals/33/ef/ea/33efeab3db1b221866f723fbf1a98c1a.png" alt="Skeletons">
    </a>

    <a href="#regk">
      <img src="https://preview.redd.it/high-stats-for-the-cost-knight-is-played-36-times-non-evo-v0-oew2buiych8f1.png?width=640&crop=smart&auto=webp&s=bfd1ac09a049b07579e13c6b910916e55a09d710" alt="Knight">
    </a>
  </div>

  <p> <br><br>Welcome to the Clash Royale InfoSite!<br>Here, you can learn about any Clash Royale Character you want, A-Z!<br>Just click on the Character and all the info you need to know is there!<br><br>Be sure to check back when new characters and 
  
  <div id="hog" class="info">
    <h2>Hog Rider</h2>
    <p>
      Fast win-condition troop that targets buildings only. Good for last minute tower take-downs.<br>
      Evo status: none<br>
      Hero status: none
    </p>
  </div>

  <div id="mk" class="info">
    <h2>Mega Knight</h2>
    <p>
      Heavy splash troop with spawn damage and jump attacks.<br>
      Evo status: Yes, when it hits an enemy, it pushes them back<br>
      Hero status: none
    </p>
  </div>

  <div id="mp" class="info">
    <h2>Mini P.E.K.K.A</h2>
    <p>
      High single-target damage troop. Can melt tanks if it can reach them.<br>
      Evo status: none<br>
      Hero status: Yes, when the bar on his head is full, he levels up for more damage and regains 40% heath.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div id="larry" class="info">
    <h2>Skeletons</h2>
    <p>
      Three low-health, single-target skeletons, named Larry, Terry, and Gerry.<br>
      Evo status: Yes, multiplys when hitting an enemy<br>
      Hero status: none
    </p>
  </div>

  <div id="regk" class="info">
    <h2>Knight</h2>
    <p>
      Tanky ground troop with solid damage.<br>
      Evo status: Yes, lands hits faster.<br>
      Hero status: Yes, spawns a sheild for 1 Elixir.
    </p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
